Package: lindasR
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Querying the Swiss Federal Linked Data Service
        'LINDAS'
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R: 
    person(
      "David", "Zumbach",
      email = "david.zumbach@gfzb.ch",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
Description: Provides convenient access to the Swiss Federal Linked Data
    Service (LINDAS) via its SPARQL endpoint (<https://ld.admin.ch/>).
    The package allows users to discover datasets, retrieve observation
    data from RDF cubes, perform full-text searches across literals,
    and work with multilingual metadata using configurable language
    preferences.
URL: https://ld.admin.ch, https://github.com/zumbov2/lindas
BugReports: https://github.com/zumbov2/lindas/issues
